Grandfather was very found of animals.He had his own zoo.Once while travelling to the market he saw a small little monkey with the tonga
driver.The poor monkey was tied to stick with bowl of water and food.The monkey looked cute so, the grandfather was lured to buy it.
He bought it for 5 rupees.Grandmother didn't like hen the grandfather kept bringing new pets. So the monkey named Toto was to be kept
hidden from Grandmother. So he was kept in a cupboard tied to a nail.